### AUTH: Register
POST {{backend_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "kgkaudi",
  "email": "kostaskgkaudi@gmail.com",
  "password": "Ectoras01!",
  "companyName": "Kostas Company AB",
  "companyAddress": "Gustav Dalensgatan 6, Göteborg"
}

###

### AUTH: Verify Email (paste verificationToken from register response)
POST {{backend_HostAddress}}/api/auth/verify-email?token={{verificationToken}}

###

### AUTH: Login
POST {{backend_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "kgkaudi",
  "password": "Ectoras01!"
}

###

### AUTH: Request Password Reset
POST {{backend_HostAddress}}/api/auth/request-password-reset
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "alice@example.com"
}

###

### AUTH: Reset Password (paste resetToken from previous response)
POST {{backend_HostAddress}}/api/auth/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "{{resetToken}}",
  "newPassword": "NewPassword123!"
}

###

### AUTH: Change Password (requires Bearer token)
POST {{backend_HostAddress}}/api/auth/change-password
Authorization: Bearer {{signinToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "currentPassword": "NewPassword123!",
  "newPassword": "AnotherPassword123!"
}

###

### AUTH: Delete Account
DELETE {{backend_HostAddress}}/api/auth/delete-account
Authorization: Bearer {{signinToken}}

###

### PRODUCTS: Get My Products
GET {{backend_HostAddress}}/api/products/mine
Authorization: Bearer {{signinToken}}

###

### PRODUCTS: Create Product
POST {{backend_HostAddress}}/api/products
Authorization: Bearer {{signinToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Pallet Jack",
  "description": "Hydraulic pallet jack",
  "dimensions": "120x80x30",
  "price": 2499.99,
  "weight": 85.5
}

###

### PRODUCTS: Get All Products
GET {{backend_HostAddress}}/api/products

###

### USERS: Get Users
GET {{backend_HostAddress}}/api/users
